'''萨拉·杜特尔特-卡皮奥'''（{{lang|en|Sara Duterte-Carpio}}），达沃语称'''印德·萨拉'''（{{lang|en|Inday Sara}}）；出生名'''萨拉·齐默尔曼·杜特尔特'''（{{lang|en|Sara Zimmerman Duterte}}），{{bd|1978年|5月31日||}}），[[菲律賓|菲律賓]][[政治人物|政治人物]]與[[律師|律師]]，現任[[菲律賓副總統|菲律賓副總統]]（第17任），是菲律賓史上第三位女副總統，曾兩度擔任[[达沃市|达沃市]]市长<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.sunstar.com.ph/davao/mayor-wants-be-called-inday-sara|title=Mayor wants to be called 'Inday Sara'|date=2010-07-28|newspaper=达沃日星报|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140416180623/http://www.sunstar.com.ph/davao/mayor-wants-be-called-inday-sara|archivedate=2014-04-16}}</ref>，是菲律賓第16任[[菲律賓總統|總統]][[羅德里戈·杜特爾特|羅德里戈·杜特蒂]]之長女。

== 政治生涯 ==
[[File:Sara_Duterte_interview.jpg|左]]
萨拉·杜特尔特是达沃市第一位女市长，也是达沃市政治历史上最年轻的当选者。2010年至2013年她与其父[[罗德里戈·杜特地|罗德里戈·杜特地]]交换角色，分别担任达沃市市长和副市长的职务<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.philstar.com/Article.aspx?articleId=574393&publicationSubCategoryId=67|title=Nograles subject Duterte's daughter|date=2010-07-10|newspaper=达沃日星报|accessdate=2016-09-20|archive-date=2012-09-07|archive-url=https://archive.fo/20120907233714/www.philstar.com/Article.aspx?articleId=574393&publicationSubCategoryId=67|dead-url=no}}</ref>。萨拉·杜特尔特的座右銘是：「献出所有时间为国家服务」。由於杜特尔特家族成員輪番出任達沃市市長，故合計在該市掌权逾30年之久<ref>{{cite news | url = http://mabuhaycity.com/forums/philippines-news-talk/15888-who-sara-duterte.html | title = Who is Sara Duterte | newspaper = Mabuhay City | date = 2011-07-05 | accessdate = 2016-09-20 | archive-date = 2016-08-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160823070342/http://mabuhaycity.com/forums/philippines-news-talk/15888-who-sara-duterte.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在2010年选举中，萨拉·杜特尔特以领先200,000票的压倒性优势，战胜了她父亲的长期政治对手众议长{{link-en|普洛斯彼罗·诺格拉雷斯|Prospero Nograles}}（{{lang|en|Prospero Nograles}}）。诺格拉雷斯早些时候质疑选举结果，向位于马尼拉的选举委员会提出抗议，声称这是杜特尔特与当地选举官员的“阴谋”<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.philstar.com/Article.aspx?articleId=574393&publicationSubCategoryId=67 | title = Nograles subject Duterte's daughter | newspaper = 达沃日星报 | date = 2010-07-10 | accessdate = 2016-09-20 | archive-date = 2012-09-07 | archive-url = https://archive.fo/20120907233714/www.philstar.com/Article.aspx?articleId=574393&publicationSubCategoryId=67 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

在就职演讲中，萨拉·杜特尔特坦言想当一名儿科医生，而不是政治家。“我从没想过要当一名政治家，但今天我作为一个市长在你们面前发言，”她说。在演讲的一个多小时里，市政厅门口的台阶上站满了人，他们希望在萨拉·杜特尔特就职演说后与她合影<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.mindanews.com/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=3183 | title = Sara Duterte | newspaper = MindaNews.com | date = 2010-07-10 | accessdate = 2016-09-21 | archive-date = 2010-07-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100709222417/http://www.mindanews.com/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=3183 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2011年，萨拉·杜特尔特引起争议，她多次殴打一名坚持拆除达沃市马兰·索利曼有财产争议的房屋的法院警长<ref>{{cite news | url = http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/20369/davao-mayor-punches-sheriff-over-demolition-of-shanties-2 | title = Davao mayor Duterte punches sheriff over demolition of shanties | newspaper = 菲律宾每日询问者报 | date = 2011-07-01 | accessdate = 2016-09-21 | archive-date = 2021-03-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210324063329/https://newsinfo.inquirer.net/20369/davao-mayor-punches-sheriff-over-demolition-of-shanties-2 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2014年，印德·萨拉·杜特尔特在Quimpo大道超速被交警抓捕。Quimpo大道限速40公里每小时（㎞/h），但她的车速达到了57㎞/h。有消息来源表示，交警最开始犹豫要不要对杜特尔特执法，但萨拉咬定交警在她超速后没收了她的驾照<ref>{{cite news | url = http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/563355/dutertes-daughter-apprehended-for-overspeeding-in-davao-city | title = Ex-Davao mayor fined for speeding | newspaper = 菲律宾每日询问者报 | date = 2014-01-15 | accessdate = 2016-09-21 | archive-date = 2021-03-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210309153527/https://newsinfo.inquirer.net/563355/dutertes-daughter-apprehended-for-overspeeding-in-davao-city | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.rappler.com/nation/47982-davao-ex-mayor-duterte-caught-for-overspeeding | title = Only in Davao: Ex-mayor Duterte caught for speeding | newspaper = Rappler | date = 2014-01-15 | accessdate = 2016-09-21 | archive-date = 2020-02-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200215110039/https://www.rappler.com/nation/47982-davao-ex-mayor-duterte-caught-for-overspeeding | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

萨拉·杜特尔特在2014年被选举为[[菲律宾红十字会|菲律宾红十字会]]九名理事之一<ref>{{cite news | url = http://archive.sunstar.com.ph/davao/local-news/2014/01/28/sara-duterte-elected-red-cross-nat-l-board-325433 | title = Sara Duterte elected to Red Cross nat’l board | newspaper = 达沃日星报 | date = 2014-01-28 | accessdate = 2016-09-21 | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304045906/http://archive.sunstar.com.ph/davao/local-news/2014/01/28/sara-duterte-elected-red-cross-nat-l-board-325433 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

儘管起初感到犹豫和反对，但在2015年10月，萨拉·杜特尔特剃光头发说服她的父亲羅德里戈·杜特尔特竞选下屆[[菲律宾总统|菲律宾总统]]，其父一開始因为缺乏[[竞选资金|竞选资金]]和{{link-en|政治机器|Political machine}}而未表态，但最後還是毅然決定投入[[2016年菲律賓總統選舉|2016年菲律賓總統選舉]]競選總統並取得勝選<ref>{{cite news|title=Inday Sara shaves head in support of Duterte's presidential run|url=http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/540625/news/nation/inday-sara-shaves-head-in-support-of-duterte-s-presidential-run|accessdate=2016-01-06|publisher=全球媒体艺术新闻在线|date=2015-10-14|archive-date=2016-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160920014444/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/540625/news/nation/inday-sara-shaves-head-in-support-of-duterte-s-presidential-run|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Hegina|first1=Aries Joseph|title=LOOK: Did Sara Duterte shave head to urge pa to run for president?|url=http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/730845/look-did-sara-duterte-shave-head-to-urge-pa-to-run-for-president|accessdate=2016-01-06|publisher=菲律宾每日询问者报|date=2015-10-14|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108132821/https://newsinfo.inquirer.net/730845/look-did-sara-duterte-shave-head-to-urge-pa-to-run-for-president|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

萨拉·杜特尔特又在2016年竞选达沃市市长，并最終當選，接替其父第二次出任达沃市市长。

在[[2022年菲律宾总统选举|2022年菲律宾大选]]中，萨拉·杜特尔特与[[小费迪南德·马科斯|小费迪南德·马科斯]]搭档参选并击败其他竞争对手当选新一任[[菲律宾副总统|菲律宾副总统]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://newsinfo.inquirer.net/1595200/marcos-duterte-head-for-landslide-win|title=Marcos, Duterte head for landslide win}}</ref>

== 个人生活 ==
2007年，萨拉·杜特尔特嫁给她的律师伙伴曼尼塞斯·“曼斯”·R·卡皮奥（{{lang|en|Manases "Mans" R. Carpio}}），她现在有两个孩子：昵称“沙基”（"{{lang|en|Sharky}}"）的养女和昵称“黄貂鱼”（"{{lang|en|Stingray}}"）的儿子马特奥·卢卡斯·D·卡皮奥（{{lang|en|Mateo Lucas D. Carpio}}）。<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.sunstar.com.ph/davao/local-news/2013/04/04/it-s-boy-mayor-sara-duterte-275858 | title = It’s a boy for Mayor Sara Duterte | newspaper = 达沃日星报 | date = 2013-04-04 | accessdate = 2016-09-21 | archive-date = 2015-04-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150402160014/http://www.sunstar.com.ph/davao/local-news/2013/04/04/it-s-boy-mayor-sara-duterte-275858 | dead-url = no }}</ref>曼尼塞斯是[[申诉专员|监察员]][[肯奇塔·卡皮奥-莫拉莱斯|肯奇塔·卡皮奥-莫拉莱斯]]（{{lang|en|Conchita Carpio-Morales}}）的侄子。<ref>Manases Carpio's father, Lucas (Davao City Regional Trial Court), is the brother of Conchita. {{cite news | url = http://manilastandardtoday.com/news/-main-stories/206057/morales-inhibits-self-from-dutertes-cases.html | title = Morales inhibits self from Dutertes’ cases | newspaper = 马尼拉今日标准报 | date = 2016-05-20 | access-date = 2016-09-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160610094202/http://manilastandardtoday.com/news/-main-stories/206057/morales-inhibits-self-from-dutertes-cases.html | archive-date = 2016-06-10 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

2016年4月18日，萨拉·杜特尔特在其Instagram账户上承认自己曾是一名强奸受害者。<ref>{{cite news|last1=del Callar|first1=Michaela|title=Sara Duterte says she too was raped; not offended by dad Digong's 'joke'|url=http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/563157/news/nation/sara-duterte-says-she-too-was-raped-not-offended-by-dad-digong-s-joke|accessdate=2016-04-21|publisher=全球媒体艺术|date=2016-04-18|archive-date=2016-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161008031510/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/563157/news/nation/sara-duterte-says-she-too-was-raped-not-offended-by-dad-digong-s-joke|dead-url=no}}</ref>在此之前的4月12日，萨拉的父亲罗德里戈在总统竞选活动上发表了有争议的“[[罗德里戈·杜特地#.E5.A5.B3.E5.82.B3.E6.95.99.E5.A3.AB.E4.BA.8B.E4.BB.B6|强奸言论]]”。然而，罗德里戈·杜特尔特反驳了他女儿的言论，并称她是个“戏剧女王”。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Campbell|first1=Charlie|title=The Philippine Election Front-Runner Calls His Daughter a 'Drama Queen' for Saying She Was Raped|url=http://time.com/4300382/rodrigo-duterte-philippines-daughter-rape-sara-inday-president-jacqueline-hamill/|accessdate=2016-04-21|publisher=CNN|date=2016-04-20|archive-date=2016-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160420125837/http://time.com/4300382/rodrigo-duterte-philippines-daughter-rape-sara-inday-president-jacqueline-hamill/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年8月19日，杜特尔特在达沃市{{link-en|卡达雅万节|Kadayawan Festival}}（{{lang|en|Kadayawan Festival}}）上宣布，她怀有七周的身孕，是个三胞胎。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sunstar.com.ph/davao/local-news/2016/08/19/mayor-sara-duterte-carpio-pregnant-triplets-492428 |title=Mayor Sara Duterte-Carpio pregnant with triplets |work=达沃日星报 |date=2016-08-19 |accessdate=2016-08-19 |archive-date=2018-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180109184116/http://www.sunstar.com.ph/davao/local-news/2016/08/19/mayor-sara-duterte-carpio-pregnant-triplets-492428 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2016年9月2日，她不幸流产，失去了三胞胎中的两个。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sunstar.com.ph/davao/local-news/2016/09/08/davao-city-mayor-sara-loses-2-triplets-496423 |title=Davao City Mayor Sara loses 2 of triplets |work=达沃日星报 |date=2016-09-08 |accessdate=2016-09-08 |archive-date=2018-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180109235520/http://www.sunstar.com.ph/davao/local-news/2016/09/08/davao-city-mayor-sara-loses-2-triplets-496423 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

